- Kutagira inshuti no kudakoraibikorwa hamwe na bagenzi be;
- Kwanga inshingano atabanje kugerageza cyangwa kwerekana ko adashoboye;
- Kutavuga ibyo akeneye no kutagaragaza ibimurimo;
- Kutita ku nshingano ze, kudashaka gusobanukirwa no gukuriki-rana
  amasomo;
- Kugaragaza amahane cyangwa kugira isoni zikabije mu nshuti no mu
  rugo.
